								<h1 class="post-title"><a href="http://healthmad.com/alternative/10-uses-for-peppermint-oil/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to 10 Uses for Peppermint Oil">10 Uses for Peppermint Oil</a></h1>
								<div id="ad300-title">
									
					<!--/* OpenX Javascript Tag v2.5.60-beta */-->
					
